The '''Sienar Advanced Research Division''' was a sprawling installation located several kilometers north of [[Curamelle/Legends|Curamelle]], the capital city of [[Corulag/Legends|Corulag]]. [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]] used this installation to design, build, and test [[TIE series/Legends|TIE]] prototypes. Security at this location was tight, and a wing of [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]] based out of Curamelle guarded the airspace above it. Residents of the area occasionally saw odd-looking [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] flying from this installation. Students of the nearby [[Dammon University]] who were foolish enough to describe these strange sightings on the galaxywide newsnet disappeared soon after making their reports.

